OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,FResearch on oil and gas in the North
OL,7,FSea "demonstrates the utter madness"
OL,8,Fof the SNP and Labour's opposition to
OL,9,Fdrilling, Kemi Badenoch has said.
OL,11,FThe Conservative leader's comments
OL,12,Fcame as a study by the University of
OL,13,FAberdeen revealed there are reserves
OL,14,Fof oil and gas in the area west of
OL,15,FShetland of 4.7 billion barrels of oil
OL,16,Fequivalent (boe).
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
