OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780617775
OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,FMs Badenoch said the survey
OL,7,Fdemonstrates the "utter madness" of
OL,8,Fthe stance taken by Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fand John Swinney to oppose drilling in
OL,10,Fthe North Sea.
OL,12,FShe said: "It defies belief that
OL,13,FLabour and the SNP won't drill our own
OL,14,Foil and gas in the North Sea when
OL,15,Findependent reports have found there
OL,16,Fare billions of barrels lying untapped.
OL,18,F"The University of Aberdeen survey
OL,19,Fjust demonstrates the utter madness of
OL,20,Fthe stance taken by Keir Starmer and
OL,21,FJohn Swinney.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@`O]tD@KOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
