PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780617775
OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,F"Domestic oil and gas are vital to the
OL,7,Fnation's energy security, as well as
OL,8,Fbeing the economic lifeblood of the
OL,9,FNorth East. Yet the industry is on its
OL,10,Fknees due to the windfall tax and the
OL,11,Fban on new developments. The
OL,12,FConservatives would scrap both
OL,13,Fimmediately."
OL,15,FMs Badenoch is joining Scottish
OL,16,FConservative leader Russell Findlay
OL,17,Fand the party's candidate, Douglas
OL,18,FLumsden, on a visit to an oil and gas
OL,19,Femployer in the Aberdeen South
OL,20,Fconstituency on Friday ahead of the by-
OL,21,Felection on June 18.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
