OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780617775
OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,FMs Badenoch said: "The Aberdeen South
OL,7,Fby-election is a referendum on the
OL,8,Ffuture of oil and gas ` and voters
OL,9,Fknow that the Conservatives will
OL,10,Falways have workers' backs.
OL,12,F"Only Douglas Lumsden, who worked in
OL,13,Fthe oil and gas industry, can beat the
OL,14,FSNP. By voting for Douglas, voters can
OL,15,Fsend a clear message to the
OL,16,Fnationalists and Labour that their war
OL,17,Fon oil and gas must end."
OL,19,FMr Findlay said Ms Badenoch is a
OL,20,F"champion" of Scotland's oil and gas
OL,21,Fsector ahead of meeting her on Friday.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUyD@YO]|D@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
