OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,FHe said: "It will be great welcoming
OL,7,FKemi back to the North East, where
OL,8,Fpeople know she's a champion of our
OL,9,Foil and gas sector, which is on life
OL,10,Fsupport due to Labour and SNP
OL,11,Fopposition to new drilling.
OL,13,F"This by-election is a golden
OL,14,Fopportunity for people in Aberdeen
OL,15,FSouth to oppose this idiotic, economic
OL,16,Fself-harm.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
