SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780617775
OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,F"The only way to do that is to vote
OL,7,Ffor Douglas Lumsden. This contest is a
OL,8,Fstraight fight between the Scottish
OL,9,FConservatives and the SNP ` and voting
OL,10,Ffor any other party risks the sleazy
OL,11,Fnationalists winning by default.
OL,13,F"That's what happened in the
OL,14,Fcorresponding Holyrood seat, when the
OL,15,Fpro-UK vote split. We can't let that
OL,16,Fhappen again."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@NO]
