OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,FRichard Thomson, SNP candidate for
OL,7,FAberdeen South, said: "The Tories'
OL,8,Flegacy in Aberdeen is thousands of oil
OL,9,Fand gas jobs lost thanks to the
OL,10,FTories' tax on our energy.
OL,12,F"By putting Scotland's energy in
OL,13,FScotland's hands, we can take sensible
OL,14,Flicensing decisions based on
OL,15,FScotland's needs with energy security,
OL,16,Fjobs and net-zero compatibility being
OL,17,Fpart of that consideration.
OL,26,@oD@WOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
