PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780617775
OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,F"Cleary we should prioritise domestic
OL,7,Fsupply over carbon intensive imports
OL,8,Fand we should never find ourselves
OL,9,Fweakening sanctions on Russian oil
OL,10,Flike Westminster has done.
OL,12,F"Just like the Reform party, the
OL,13,FTories couldn't care less about our
OL,14,Foil and gas industry, they care about
OL,15,Fmilking every last penny out of it
OL,16,Fwithout investing anything back ` #400
OL,17,Fbillion has been syphoned off by these
OL,18,Fcrooks in Westminster and only the SNP
OL,19,Fwould use our vast energy wealth to
OL,20,Fprotect Scottish jobs and build a
OL,21,Fwealthier, independent, country."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU}D@aO]
