OL,3,CBadenoch: Study shows 'utter madness'
OL,4,Cof SNP and Labour on North Sea drilling
OL,6,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Issuing new licences to explore new
OL,8,Ffields cannot give us energy security
OL,9,Fand will not take a penny off bills.
OL,11,F"The lesson of yet another fossil fuel
OL,12,Fcrisis is the UK needs to get off the
OL,13,Ffossil fuel rollercoaster and onto
OL,14,Fclean homegrown power we control."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@bO]
